replies.body:
Why? You are restricted anyways...

**And also chat should be removed completely**;
 There are torrents of toxicity coming out of that portal, called "chat window", straight from the depths of hell. 
I have lost so many games because a teammate couldn't resist its power and was pushed to the brink of madness by its taunting calls and screams.

They should only allow emoticons, plus game items and champ icons like here.

{{champion:48}}
